Download the https://github.com/carlosmccosta/pcl (master-all-ptr branch)
Compile it. Since I am using the catkin tool build and its chain depend a create a ws_common with the create_ws scripts.
Then i set the catkin profile to debug, compile it and then to release and compile it.

Create the ws_drl

clone the following

https://github.com/ros-perception/pcl_msgs
https://github.com/carlosmccosta/pose_to_tf_publisher
https://github.com/carlosmccosta/laserscan_to_pointcloud
https://github.com/ros-perception/perception_pcl  (melodic devel)
https://github.com/carlosmccosta/point_cloud_io.git


After it set the gedit with the path to drl_ws
Than clone inside the drl ws

https://github.com/carlosmccosta/dynamic_robot_localization
https://github.com/carlosmccosta/object_recognition.git


Compile again

Rode o script install/a.dependences.

setting the ws to debug and extende it:
catkin profile set debug
catkin config --extend /home/joaopedro/ros_ws/ws_common/devel_release/

catkin profile set debug
catkin config --extend /home/joaopedro/ros_ws/ws_common/devel_debug/

compile ambos perfis
